    What is little kids in shoes?
    Baby sizes 0-3.5 typically fit ages 0-11 months. Toddler sizes 4-10 typically fit ages 1-3 years. Little kids' sizes 10.5-3 typically fit ages 4-8 years. Big kids' sizes 3.5-7 typically fit ages 8+. Around the ages of 9-12, many kids begin to grow into adult sizes.

    Which is the number one footwear brand in India?
    AI Overview
    Bata and Metro Brands are among the top footwear brands in India. 
    Bata
    • Bata is a leading footwear retailer in India. 
    • Bata offers a wide range of shoes for different occasions. 
    • Bata is known for its quality, comfort, and style. 
    • Bata was founded in 1931 as Bata Shoe Company Private Limited. 
    • Bata has a manufacturing facility in Batanagar that was the first in India to receive ISO: 9001 certifications. 
    Metro Brands 
    • As of February 2025, Metro Brands was the leading footwear company in India by market capitalization.
    Other top footwear brands in India: 
    Inc. 5, Regal Shoes, Adidas, Puma, Skechers, Nike, Reebok, New Balance, and ASICS.
    When choosing a footwear brand, you can consider things like: Brand reputation, Customer reviews, Customer base, and Brand loyalty metrics.
